### Phase 1 (Weeks 1-4): Read-Only Integration
- Deploy fitness assessment engine
- Establish one-way data flow to scheduling system (log only)
- Implement supervisor dashboard views

### Phase 2 (Weeks 5-8): Protocol Compliance
