Models extend prior specifications (e.g., Supported-Duty Track Model from DASH-004, Baseline Metrics from DASH-001, and CCI Model from DASH-004). New models define the referral summary and physician request. All use JSON Schema with encryption (AES-256) and HIPAA-compliant handling assumptions.

